title: Herby Roasted Chicken and Pork Ribs with Honey-Mustard Brussels Sprouts and Garlicky Smashed Potatoes
description: We've got you covered for your next special night in with this dish! A brush of thyme and parsley oil creates fragrant, juicy roasted chicken served alongside creamy garlic-butter smashed potatoes, roasted Brussels sprouts and tender pork ribs. It's sure to be unforgettably delicious!
